data.description:
Come and see this big CORNER house with lots of possibilities. One story home with 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms and 1 additional room with no permit. Used to be a duplex,
with 2 addresses, 2 PG&E meters and 2 mailboxes and the previous owner converted this to SINGLE FAMILY RESIDENSE per the seller. You can change this back to a DUPLEX (make sure to check 
with the county). This home sits on  8,276 sq.ft. corner lot, and 3,395 sq ft. living area, and built in 1983. Perfect for big families, investment or business. Use your imagination as to what you want to do
on this huge corner house. As Is Sale, and please use your due deligence.
